  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK436">
<l>taṉkuṟṟa nīkkip piṟarkuṟṟaṅ kāṇkiṟpiṉ </l>
<l>eṉkuṟṟa māku miṟaikku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What fault will remain in the king who has put away his own evils, and looks after the evils of others.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
